    "media:imagetext": "VIEW OF TULSA MUNCIPAL AIRPORT,\nTULSA, OKLA.\nTulsa's Municipal\nAirport has been self-sustaining\nsince its inception in 1928.\nThere are more miles of\nconcrete runways on this airport than on any other\nairport in the United States.\nprofit from airport operation has been returned\nto the aviation\nindustry in the form of better im-\nprovements.\nThis has resulted in Tulsa having one\nof the\nmost\nmodern\nairports in America\nand,\npresent, has the highest government rating obtainable.\nP2151\n50\nPlace\nSTAMP\nHere\nPost Card\n2015.166.2377",
